      <div type="letter" xml:id="d4e41">
        <pb n="1" facs="0012_000117_000202_0001.jpg" xml:id="d4e42"/>
        <p>New Orleans Jun 18</p>
        <p><unclear reason="illegible" resp="bds">Free</unclear> Robert Allen</p>
        <p>Major David Burford</p>
        <p>
          <unclear reason="illegible" resp="bds">Cartage T.</unclear>
        </p>
        <p>Washington D.C.</p>
        <p>April 15 1820</p>
        <pb n="2" facs="0012_000117_000202_0002.jpg" xml:id="d4e59"/>
        <p>Washington</p>
        <p>April 15th 1820</p>
        <p>Dear Sir</p>
        <p>I send you the Enclosed letter to put you on your guard from running into the same Error or putting yourself in the power of these <unclear reason="illegible" resp="bds">Swindlers</unclear> Sell at Orleans if you get but two cents pr pound - I have no hopes that any thing I can say will be <unclear reason="illegible" resp="bds">attend</unclear> to by <unclear reason="illegible" resp="bds">Mr. Chester</unclear> who seems bent on destruction</p>
        <p>you will notice <unclear reason="illegible" resp="bds">his</unclear> people priced my tobacco at 8 cents <unclear reason="illegible" resp="bds">&amp;</unclear> took <unclear reason="illegible" resp="bds">commissory &amp;</unclear> accordingly by now it <unclear reason="illegible" resp="bds">nets me</unclear> about three cents I cannot think or talk of <unclear reason="illegible" resp="bds">my</unclear> cursed unfortunate <unclear reason="illegible" resp="bds">businesses</unclear> which is to Ruin me without my <unclear reason="illegible" resp="bds">Judgement</unclear> or wishes consulted in most <unclear reason="illegible" resp="bds">afet</unclear>
            </p>
        <p>your friend Robert Allen</p>
      </div>
    </body>
